column5: Charming home, very open and bright living space! This fabulous home offers 3 bdrm, 1 office room, 2 baths, and 2 living spaces in the front. The space is very well utilized: large living room with cozy woodburning fireplace & numerous windows provide natural light. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms.
column8: Lovely 3 bdrm house near the lake Lewisville
